Setting 
\begin_inset Formula $V=V_{T}$
\end_inset

, we find the threshold current 
\begin_inset Formula $I_{T}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
0 & =-g_{L}(V_{T}-V_{L})+\psi(V_{T})+I_{T}\\
I_{T} & =g_{L}(V_{T}-V_{L})-\psi(V_{T})
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset

 
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

